Package com.bignerdranch.android.geoquiz

Contains classes that create an Android application that quizzes users on their geography knowledge.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BooleanQuestion
    A class representing a single question with a boolean answer (true or false).
    CheatActivity
    A class representing an activity in which users can cheat by viewing the answer to the current quiz question.
    QuizActivity
    A class representing an activity in which users' geography knowledge is tested with a series of True/False questions.
